292
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:17,660
So annoying.

293
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:31,500
Who is it?

294
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:34,220
Who...

295
00:11:35,460 --> 00:11:36,460
Who?

296
00:11:39,340 --> 00:11:40,340
Who is it?

297
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:50,700
Oh, it's you.

298
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:53,020
