300
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:56,500
That's so rude.

301
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:57,700
What's the matter?

302
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:03,940
You...

303
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:05,220
What are you doing?

304
00:12:06,020 --> 00:12:06,980
You...

305
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:11,460
Cuiying, Cuiying.

306
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:13,740
You...

307
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:15,780
What do you want?

308
00:12:15,780 --> 00:12:17,620
Madam, I'm here.

309
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,100
Mother.

310
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:22,500
Please, save Jing Kan.

311
00:12:29,580 --> 00:12:30,980
How can I save him?

312
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:32,980
Mother,

313
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:35,020
Jing Kan carries

314
00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:36,620
Father's blood.

315
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:39,620
Even if you don't consider him,

316
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,740
consider his father.

317
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:44,780
Half of his blood belongs to the master.

318
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:47,020
What about the other half?

319
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:48,300
The other half...

320
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,700
The other half

321
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:55,460
belongs to tea.

322
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:01,220
Mother...

323
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,060
I've never regarded you

324
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:04,140
as my daughter-in-law.

325
00:13:07,020 --> 00:13:08,220
That's fine.

326
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:10,380
If you can save Jing Kan,

327
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:11,700
do whatever you want.

328
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:13,100
I beg you.

329
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:15,980
Begging won't work.

330
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:20,140
I've heard of this.

331
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:23,980
The tea permit is so important.

332
00:13:24,460 --> 00:13:25,580
Jing Kan

333
00:13:26,260 --> 00:13:28,140
was too careless.

334
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:31,660
So, you set him off?

335
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:34,180
I...

336
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,860
Who said so?

337
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:37,580
Do you have any proof?

338
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,900
Yes, Cuiying is right.

339
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:42,780
How could Mother treat her own son

340
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:44,180
with such cruelty,

341
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:45,060
spite, and malice

342
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:46,380
by having him imprisoned?

343
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:47,620
The mastermind

344
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:48,620
will surely be punished.

345
00:13:48,620 --> 00:13:49,580
Stop, stop.

346
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:52,580
Why curse others like that?

347
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,140
What I mean is...

348
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:58,220
Mother,

349
00:13:59,100 --> 00:14:00,620
please help Jing Kan this time.

350
00:14:01,060 --> 00:14:02,060
He knows he's wrong.

351
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:08,260
I'd like to help him,

352
00:14:08,660 --> 00:14:09,620
but think about it.

353
00:14:10,020 --> 00:14:11,340
If I save him,

354
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:12,700
when will he

355
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:13,980
ever grow?

356
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:15,140
But if you don't help him,

357
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:16,260
he won't live to grow.

358
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,580
That would be his fate.

359
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:26,620
So, you decide

360
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:27,780
to watch him die?

361
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:31,380
You can't kneel anymore?

362
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:34,340
If you're willing to help Jing Kan,

363
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:36,240
I'll kneel here as long as it takes.

364
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:38,360
But Grandmother is not at home now.

365
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:40,580
If someone takes advantage of this

366
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:42,340
to plot against Jing Kan,

367
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:44,460
I won't agree to it.

368
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:46,140
Who are you threatening?

369
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:48,860
You're a married couple.

370
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:50,500
You should act like this.

371
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:53,140
I will not give up on Jing Kan.

372
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,220
Listen...

373
00:15:02,220 --> 00:15:04,900
Who'd be so wicked to set such a trap?

374
00:15:08,940 --> 00:15:11,500
(Jing Residence)

375
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:12,500
Milady.

376
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,500
I heard from Mingyue

377
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:15,220
that Ms. Luo just wants to punish him

378
00:15:15,220 --> 00:15:16,340
as a warning.

379
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:17,860
She feared the Old Lady

380
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:19,500
would not let it go.

381
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:21,220
Are you sure?

382
00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:22,380
Absolutely.

383
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:23,820
She heard it when she went

384
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:24,740
to deliver tea.

385
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:28,740
Did she

386
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:30,740
tell anyone else about this?

387
00:15:30,740 --> 00:15:31,780
Probably not.

388
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:32,860
We talked about it

389
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:33,780
while washing clothes.

390
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:35,020
That's good.

391
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:36,020
Tell her

392
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:37,100
not to tell others.

393
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:41,460
