394
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:42,380
How can I stop her

395
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:43,940
from telling others?

396
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:45,980
Aren't you friends?

397
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:47,140
She won't even agree to that?

398
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,540
What kind of friendship is this?

399
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:52,860
So, how can we

400
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:54,420
keep her quiet?

401
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:00,420
My goodness.

402
00:16:00,820 --> 00:16:01,780
So desperate for money.

403
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:02,780
All of you are like this.

404
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:06,500
Give it to her.

405
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:08,460
Thanks, milady.

406
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,660
Why stand there? Go.

407
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:13,180
Milady.

408
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:14,340
Isn't there one more?

409
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:21,100
So desperate for money. Go.

410
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:22,060
Thanks, milady.

411
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:24,180
I don't have

412
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:26,460
much left.

413
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:38,660
What?

414
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:40,260
What do you mean?

415
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:41,940
What do you want?

416
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,380
Milady,

417
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,180
we won't tell anyone.

418
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:49,340
So many thieves at home.

419
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:56,660
Sixi,

420
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:58,500
this is all the money we have now.

421
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:00,660
Is it enough to bribe Magistrate Meng?

422
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:02,820
It'd be okay if he were three.

423
00:17:04,020 --> 00:17:04,940
This won't even stuff

424
00:17:04,940 --> 00:17:06,460
that official's mouth.

425
00:17:09,140 --> 00:17:10,100
Guiwei,

426
00:17:10,940 --> 00:17:11,940
take this letter

427
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:13,420
to Songxi County and find Yu.

428
00:17:13,740 --> 00:17:14,660
He knows many people.

429
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:15,620
Let him think of a way.

430
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:16,940
Come on.

431
00:17:17,260 --> 00:17:18,940
You're also hanging by a thread.

432
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:20,260
Take care of yourself first.

433
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:21,940
I'm fine, at least for now.

434
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:23,060
Just listen to me.

435
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:28,100
Shall we break into the prison?

436
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,460
Great.

437
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:30,820
We'll all die together.

438
00:17:30,820 --> 00:17:31,940
How lively.

439
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:33,940
Zhu.

440
00:17:34,580 --> 00:17:35,780
- Zhenzhu.
- Zhen.

441
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:37,060
- Zhenzhu.
- Zhenzhu.

442
00:17:37,060 --> 00:17:37,940
Show me some respect.

443
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,700
Zhenzhu, we're very worried.

444
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:40,940
Don't interrupt, okay?

445
00:17:42,740 --> 00:17:43,740
You

446
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:45,580
are lucky

447
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:46,620
to have met me.

448
00:17:47,340 --> 00:17:48,300
How so?

449
00:17:48,740 --> 00:17:49,780
Honestly,

450
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,220
although I usually

451
00:17:52,460 --> 00:17:55,900
don't get along with Jing Kan,

452
00:17:55,930 --> 00:17:56,820
we grew up

453
00:17:56,820 --> 00:17:58,020
together after all.

454
00:17:58,500 --> 00:17:59,780
Seeing him like this

455
00:18:00,100 --> 00:18:01,180
makes me sad.

456
00:18:03,260 --> 00:18:04,660
Has your uncle been reinstated?

457
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:05,980
Don't worry about that.

458
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:08,700
Listen, I'll help you.

459
00:18:09,100 --> 00:18:10,060
Really?

460
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:11,860
You don't trust me? Bye.

461
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,260
Zhenzhu.

462
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,180
I mean what I said.

463
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:17,300
If you can get Jing Kan out,

464
00:18:17,820 --> 00:18:18,780
I'll give you the shop.

465
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:19,780
Good.

466
00:18:20,380 --> 00:18:22,300
With that temper of yours,

467
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:23,740
we're surely bound as sisters.

468
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:25,420
So, how do you plan to save him?

469
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:32,700
I have connections in the yamen.

470
00:18:33,340 --> 00:18:34,460
Who, your uncle?

471
00:18:34,460 --> 00:18:35,460
No.

472
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:36,900
Everyone has

473
00:18:36,900 --> 00:18:37,820
their own methods.

474
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:39,380
In short, I've pulled some strings,

475
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:40,380
so just

476
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,460
rest assured.

477
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:42,500
Bye.

478
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:43,500
I'll see you off.

479
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:44,580
No need.

480
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:45,700
I'm here.

481
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:48,220
Thanks, Zhu.

482
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,220
Move aside.

483
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:58,060
(Intoxicating Spring)

484
00:18:58,060 --> 00:19:01,380
(Taiping Government)

485
00:19:12,500 --> 00:19:13,460
Milord, milord.

486
00:19:13,460 --> 00:19:14,940
Don't sleep yet.

487
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:16,500
Milord,

488
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:18,140
the Jings sent someone

489
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:20,180
with 100 jin of rice,

490
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,740
