494
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,660
Am I that cheap?

495
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:31,940
Milord, milord.

496
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:35,100
It's as easy as pie for you.

497
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:36,860
Alright, behead him.

498
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,020
Milord, milord.

499
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:39,140
What are you doing?

500
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:40,420
You can't behead him.

501
00:19:40,420 --> 00:19:41,740
They want you

502
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:42,860
to have mercy on him.

503
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:43,940
You got it wrong.

504
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:45,660
You should be clearer.

505
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:46,700
Then release him.

506
00:19:46,700 --> 00:19:47,700
Milord, milord.

507
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,900
The Jings don't want you

508
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:51,380
to release him so easily.

509
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,340
They want you

510
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:53,940
to punish him first.

511
00:19:53,980 --> 00:19:55,500
Then release him after beheading him.

512
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:57,100
No, milord.

513
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:59,220
What exactly do they want?

514
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:00,620
Please calm down, milord.

515
00:20:00,620 --> 00:20:01,500
Do I have to guess

516
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:02,660
what favor they want?

517
00:20:02,820 --> 00:20:03,700
Am I the magistrate

518
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:05,180
to serve them?

519
00:20:05,860 --> 00:20:06,700
Milord.

520
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:07,540
Alright.

521
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:08,540
Behead him.

522
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:10,860
I'll see if Jing Kan can withstand it.

523
00:20:10,970 --> 00:20:11,820
We've taken the money.

524
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:13,020
Say another word

525
00:20:13,380 --> 00:20:14,500
and we'll behead you, too.

526
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,100
Get out.

527
00:20:16,100 --> 00:20:17,060
Yes.

528
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:19,500
(Heavenly Feathers)

529
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:20,500
Milady.

530
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:22,380
- Drink.
- Careful.

531
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:23,540
I'll drink.

532
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,020
I'll surely outdrink them.

533
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:26,220
Watch the step.

534
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:27,740
So drunk again.

535
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:29,100
Be careful.

536
00:20:29,580 --> 00:20:30,540
Slow down.

537
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:31,780
Quick, there, there.

538
00:20:31,820 --> 00:20:32,880
I'll surely outdrink you.

539
00:20:34,020 --> 00:20:35,020
Drink.

540
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:36,100
Milady.

541
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:37,220
Why are you so drunk?

542
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,320
I'll surely outdrink them.

543
00:20:38,660 --> 00:20:40,220
I'll fetch you a soup to sober up.

544
00:20:41,220 --> 00:20:42,220
No need.

545
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:49,940
Do I look drunk?

546
00:20:50,380 --> 00:20:51,340
I suppose...

547
00:20:51,820 --> 00:20:52,780
so.

548
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:54,700
This little wine

549
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:56,180
won't faze me.

550
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,540
Milady,

551
00:20:58,540 --> 00:20:59,540
who did you drink

552
00:20:59,540 --> 00:21:00,700
