553
00:21:02,340 --> 00:21:04,260
Those women at the Tea Guild

554
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:07,380
looked down on me.

555
00:21:07,780 --> 00:21:08,660
One said

556
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:09,500
her husband

557
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:10,660
was so powerful.

558
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:12,060
Another said

559
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:14,140
her mother was so powerful.

560
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:16,420
As if they themselves were so powerful.

561
00:21:16,580 --> 00:21:17,800
They just shamed me like that.

562
00:21:18,180 --> 00:21:19,140
Listen.

563
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:20,540
I've spread the word.

564
00:21:20,780 --> 00:21:22,100
The Anping Bridge Shop

565
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:24,740
will reopen in ten days.

566
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:26,820
Milady,

567
00:21:26,820 --> 00:21:27,780
why take them

568
00:21:27,780 --> 00:21:28,900
seriously?

569
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:29,860
Go.

570
00:21:30,580 --> 00:21:31,780
Go fetch Ai Sixi.

571
00:21:32,780 --> 00:21:33,900
You want to drink more?

572
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:35,940
I must let her see it.

573
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,580
I want her to see

574
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:39,700
how I've racked my brains

575
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:41,260
and risked my life,

576
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:42,500
working day and night,

577
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,700
to save her husband.

578
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:45,940
If she's moved,

579
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:47,300
she'd give me the shop at once.

580
00:21:47,460 --> 00:21:48,380
Milady,

581
00:21:48,380 --> 00:21:49,780
you drank so much

582
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:50,740
for Ai Sixi?

583
00:21:51,260 --> 00:21:52,260
My goodness.

584
00:21:52,300 --> 00:21:53,380
You're such a fool.

585
00:21:55,620 --> 00:21:56,540
Never mind.

586
00:21:56,540 --> 00:21:57,540
Just go fetch her.

587
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:00,160
- Okay.
- Hurry.

588
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:11,140
Not comfortable enough.

589
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:18,740
So good.

590
00:22:24,700 --> 00:22:27,780
Ai Sixi.

