00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:34,940
Ai Sixi...

592
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:48,740
Why isn't she here yet?

593
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:53,980
- Milady, she's here.
- Ai Sixi.

594
00:22:54,140 --> 00:22:55,100
Zhu,

595
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:56,780
how much did you drink?

596
00:22:56,780 --> 00:22:59,700
I drank for my good cousin,

597
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:02,620
- Jing Kan.
- I'll get you some water.

598
00:23:02,620 --> 00:23:03,580
I'll get you some water.

599
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:05,700
I'll drink as much

600
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:08,100
as I need.

601
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:09,380
Drink some water.

602
00:23:10,180 --> 00:23:11,860
I don't want it.

603
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:14,620
- Come on.
- Careful.

604
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:15,740
Ai Sixi...

605
00:23:16,660 --> 00:23:17,620
Ai...

606
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:19,980
Drink some water.

607
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:32,940
Why did you come alone?

608
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:36,220
My cousin is drunk, too.

609
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:37,860
She's going wild in her room.

610
00:23:40,260 --> 00:23:41,540
Milady, milady.

611
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:44,900
Jing Kan,

612
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:47,780
I'll definitely save you.

613
00:23:57,020 --> 00:23:58,860
But how can I save you?

614
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:01,940
I don't know what to do.

615
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:03,700
I wrote to Grandmother,

616
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:05,940
but I don't know when she'll be back.

617
00:24:10,580 --> 00:24:13,620
Ai Sixi.

618
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:20,180
Ai Sixi.

619
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:22,260
Ai...

620
00:24:30,780 --> 00:24:31,780
All for nothing.

621
00:24:32,540 --> 00:24:34,940
Ai Sixi.

622
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,540
Zhenzhu, you're here.

623
00:24:37,780 --> 00:24:38,780
Sixi.

624
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:43,940
Sixi,

625
00:24:46,140 --> 00:24:47,420
you don't know

626
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:50,460
how much I suffered today.

627
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:52,860
In all my life,

628
00:24:52,860 --> 00:24:56,900
I've never drunk so much wine.

629
00:24:57,060 --> 00:24:58,100
What happened in the end?

630
00:24:58,700 --> 00:24:59,980
There's hope.

631
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:02,300
But they said

632
00:25:02,300 --> 00:25:04,860
you can't be trusted.

633
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:09,860
Give me that shop now,

634
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:13,740
or all my efforts will be in vain.

635
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:15,980
Got it.

636
00:25:20,540 --> 00:25:21,420
I've long prepared

637
00:25:21,420 --> 00:25:22,900
the transfer deed.

638
00:25:24,260 --> 00:25:25,940
You'll surely be my friend.

639
00:25:27,700 --> 00:25:29,020
It's not about trust.

640
00:25:29,780 --> 00:25:31,380
As soon as Jing Kan is released,

641
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:34,220
the deed will be yours.

642
00:25:36,580 --> 00:25:37,660
So, you...

643
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:49,940
You'll give it to me anyway.

644
00:25:51,980 --> 00:25:53,660
Fine, it's a deal.

645
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:03,220
(Spring Breeze)

646
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:08,300
Milady, you needed me?

647
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:12,220
Did Mingyue tell you

648
00:26:12,320 --> 00:26:13,700
how long Auntie's little punishment

649
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:14,940
is to last?

650
00:26:16,260 --> 00:26:18,500
Well.

651
00:26:18,500 --> 00:26:19,460
Listen.

652
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:21,180
I already told

653
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:22,100
those Tea Guild women

654
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:23,140
that my shop will reopen

655
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:25,100
in nine days.

656
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:27,220
If this can't be done,

657
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:28,620
I'll be embarrassed.

658
00:26:29,260 --> 00:26:30,300
But milady,

659
00:26:30,460 --> 00:26:31,660
Mingyue really didn't say.

660
00:26:32,460 --> 00:26:33,500
It's okay.

661
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:34,380
Then,

662
00:26:34,380 --> 00:26:35,660
tell Mingyue to persuade Auntie

663
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:36,580
and let her hurry up.

664
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:38,900
Milady, how can she do that?

665
00:26:42,780 --> 00:26:43,740
One for you.

666
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:44,860
One for Mingyue.

667
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:47,100
Money makes the millstones talk.

668
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:48,100
Go.

669
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:49,460
- Milady.
- Zhenzhu.

670
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:50,380
Go, hurry.

671
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:52,540
I was drunk last night.

672
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:54,140
You went to ask for help, right?

673
00:26:54,140 --> 00:26:55,100
Sit, Sixi.

674
00:26:55,860 --> 00:26:57,860
Don't worry. Everything's done.

675
00:26:58,020 --> 00:26:59,020
There's hope?

676
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:00,700
There's more than hope.

677
00:27:00,740 --> 00:27:02,100
He will be released at once.

678
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:03,220
That's wonderful.

679
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:04,220
Just sit there.

680
00:27:05,260 --> 00:27:06,260
No. 357.

681
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:08,500
- No. 357.
- What again?

682
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:12,620
Jing Kan...

683
00:27:13,020 --> 00:27:14,020
What did I tell you?

684
00:27:14,100 --> 00:27:15,220
Good news.

685
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:16,900
Has Jing Kan been released?

686
00:27:18,140 --> 00:27:19,340
He's been sentenced to death.

687
00:27:20,260 --> 00:27:21,140
What?

688
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:22,700
They even posted a notice.

689
00:27:28,300 --> 00:27:29,300
Jing Zhenzhu,

690
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,560
didn't you say you pulled some strings?

691
00:27:31,580 --> 00:27:33,090
You only made things worse!

692
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:34,060
I didn't.

693
00:27:34,060 --> 00:27:35,060
Who exactly did you find?

694
00:27:35,060 --> 00:27:36,060
I...

695
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:40,060
Well.

696
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:41,380
I'll just give up

697
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:42,460
that shop for now.

698
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:43,660
Come back.

699
00:27:43,660 --> 00:27:44,940
What exactly happened?

700
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:47,620
Tell me.

701
00:27:48,580 --> 00:27:49,540
I didn't find anyone.

702
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:51,380
You didn't?

703
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:53,640
I thought it was almost done,

704
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,580
so I just took advantage

705
00:27:54,580 --> 00:27:55,620
to take some credit.

706
00:27:55,620 --> 00:27:57,140
You said Auntie

707
00:27:57,140 --> 00:27:58,100
just wanted

708
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,220
to punish him, right?

709
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:00,140
Yes, yes.

710
00:28:00,140 --> 00:28:01,140
Mingyue really said so.

711
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:02,460
I didn't do anything.

712
00:28:03,780 --> 00:28:04,980
The notice is posted already?

713
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:08,700
Isn't that punishment enough?

714
00:28:09,060 --> 00:28:10,500
What more do you want?

715
00:28:12,180 --> 00:28:14,380
All the Jings are bad people!

716
00:28:19,460 --> 00:28:21,380
(Jinyu Tea)

717
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:22,780
Lately, our tea plantation

718
00:28:22,900 --> 00:28:25,260
has produced a total of 1,280 jin.

719
00:28:25,900 --> 00:28:27,140
The best-selling branch

720
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:28,420
is still our main store.

721
00:28:28,940 --> 00:28:29,980
The Wushen Temple Shop

722
00:28:30,140 --> 00:28:31,460
comes second in sales,

723
00:28:31,500 --> 00:28:33,300
followed by the Shijing Spring Shop.

724
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:35,300
Madam, Madam.

725
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:36,700
Madam, it's bad.

726
00:28:37,340 --> 00:28:39,220
What are you so flustered?

727
00:28:39,300 --> 00:28:40,420
I told you

728
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:42,740
to always remain composed.

729
00:28:44,940 --> 00:28:47,100
Jing Kan has been sentenced to death.

730
00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:48,460
What?

731
00:28:54,740 --> 00:28:56,220
Stop what you're doing.

732
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:57,500
Rest for a moment.

733
00:28:57,820 --> 00:28:58,780
Yes.

734
00:29:01,820 --> 00:29:02,860
What happened?

735
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:04,300
What should we do, Madam?

736
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:05,860
The Old Lady has returned.

737
00:29:07,220 --> 00:29:09,020
So suddenly? Why?

738
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:10,180
I don't know.

739
00:29:10,980 --> 00:29:12,740
Did you deliver 100 taels of silver

740
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:13,700
to Magistrate Meng

741
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:14,860
as I asked?

742
00:29:14,860 --> 00:29:15,820
Yes.

743
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:17,580
100 taels of high-quality silver.

744
00:29:17,580 --> 00:29:18,540
Then,

745
00:29:19,300 --> 00:29:21,020
did you say anything you shouldn't?

746
00:29:21,020 --> 00:29:22,220
No.

747
00:29:22,220 --> 00:29:23,900
I asked them

748
00:29:23,900 --> 00:29:25,460
to look after Jing Kan.

749
00:29:25,780 --> 00:29:26,940
Look after him...

750
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,380
It sounds fine.

751
00:29:28,380 --> 00:29:29,340
Yes.

752
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:31,420
What expression did you have?

753
00:29:31,740 --> 00:29:33,060
- Expression?
- Yes, expression.

754
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:36,780
Advisor Xia,

755
00:29:36,860 --> 00:29:38,860
please tell Magistrate Meng

756
00:29:39,140 --> 00:29:41,780
to look after Jing Kan.

757
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:43,660
Your expression was wrong.

758
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:44,700
Wrong expression?

759
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,220
It looked sinister.

760
00:29:46,220 --> 00:29:47,460
Impossible.

761
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:49,060
I'm not sinister.

762
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,220
I just look like this.

763
00:29:50,220 --> 00:29:51,380
Isn't that sinister?

764
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:55,900
Could it be he thought

765
00:29:55,900 --> 00:29:57,220
we gave too little money?

766
00:29:57,580 --> 00:29:58,900
Too little?

767
00:29:59,940 --> 00:30:00,900
He still

768
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:02,860
shouldn't have had murderous intent.

769
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:04,940
Those officials are unpredictable.

770
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:06,140
I told you

771
00:30:06,140 --> 00:30:07,180
to listen to me

772
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:08,460
and not to provoke them.

773
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:10,860
What's the use of saying this now?

774
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,700
What should we do now?

775
00:30:19,420 --> 00:30:22,020
Give them another 200 taels of silver

776
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:23,980
and tell Magistrate Meng

777
00:30:24,340 --> 00:30:25,740
to spare him.

778
00:30:26,220 --> 00:30:27,220
Yes.

779
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:28,260
Wait.

780
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:32,220
We must make sure no one knows

781
00:30:32,220 --> 00:30:34,500
that we're helping Jing Kan,

782
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:36,940
or what would people think?

783
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:37,780
Yes, yes.

784
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:38,780
Understood.

785
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,620
Be careful about how you do it.

786
00:30:47,180 --> 00:30:48,140
Alright.

787
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:50,900
Calm down.

788
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:52,500
Tell me about your grievances.

789
00:30:53,140 --> 00:30:54,620
Wasn't Jing Kan supposed to be exiled?

790
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:56,140
Why was he suddenly sentenced to death?

791
00:30:56,740 --> 00:30:57,940
That was decided by higher-ups.

792
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:58,860
How would I know?

793
00:30:58,860 --> 00:31:00,220
I'm going to find Magistrate Meng.

794
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:01,500
Wait.

795
00:31:02,180 --> 00:31:03,140
Let go.

796
00:31:03,860 --> 00:31:04,740
We're acquaintances.

797
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:05,700
Don't cause trouble.

798
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:06,860
Let me tell you the truth.

799
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:08,100
Someone in your family

800
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:09,740
slipped money to the higher-ups

801
00:31:09,980 --> 00:31:11,180
to handle it specially.

802
00:31:11,780 --> 00:31:12,900
Was it Jing Zhenzhu?

803
00:31:13,700 --> 00:31:15,260
I don't know who it was.

804
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:18,340
Anyway, it was someone in your family.

805
00:31:18,940 --> 00:31:21,660
Fine, if Jing Kan dies,

806
00:31:22,260 --> 00:31:23,460
no one else will live.

807
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:35,060
My Lady,

808
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,220
the letter is ready.

809
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:38,900
Take it to Lord Xu
in Anning Prefecture now

810
00:31:39,020 --> 00:31:39,900
and tell him

811
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:41,620
I'll agree to any condition

812
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:43,540
if he can save my grandson.

813
00:31:43,540 --> 00:31:44,540
Yes.

814
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,460
I just left,

815
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:51,900
and you're already plotting
against Jing Kan.

816
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,100
Who did it?

817
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:55,100
Grandmother,

818
00:31:55,100 --> 00:31:56,940
it has nothing to do with me.

819
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:59,300
Tell me. Was it her?

820
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:01,740
We don't know.

821
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,780
Tell me. Was it her?

822
00:32:04,100 --> 00:32:05,060
Mother,

823
00:32:05,300 --> 00:32:06,540
this can't have anything

824
00:32:06,780 --> 00:32:08,020
to do with Zhenzhu.

825
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:08,980
Sit down.

826
00:32:09,300 --> 00:32:10,940
I'll settle accounts with you later.

827
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:12,780
Stop stalling.

828
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:14,620
Tell us everything you know.

829
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:15,700
Tell me.

830
00:32:16,500 --> 00:32:18,220
Old Lady, please spare us.

831
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:19,620
Zhenzhu told us not to speak.

832
00:32:19,700 --> 00:32:21,220
She gave us some money

833
00:32:21,220 --> 00:32:22,500
to keep us quiet.

834
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:24,060
Zhenzhu,

835
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:25,980
what exactly did you do?

836
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:27,620
How dare you ask me?

837
00:32:27,700 --> 00:32:29,180
This all started because of you.

838
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,740
- Mingzhen.
- Yes.

839
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:36,860
Starting with Jing Zhenzhu,

840
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:38,660
hit them one by one

841
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:40,940
until they tell the truth.

842
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:42,060
Grandmother.

843
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:43,140
Go away.

844
00:32:43,140 --> 00:32:43,990
Stop, Sixi.

845
00:32:43,990 --> 00:32:45,460
You bunch of jerks.

846
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:46,780
I'll fight you all.

847
00:32:48,220 --> 00:32:49,740
What are you doing?

848
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:51,100
Ai Sixi has gone mad.

849
00:32:51,100 --> 00:32:53,500
Why can't you accommodate Jing Kan?

850
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:54,900
Why must you kill him?

851
00:32:55,020 --> 00:32:56,540
Sixi, calm down.

852
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,660
Sixi,

853
00:32:57,660 --> 00:32:58,660
as long as I'm here,

854
00:32:58,860 --> 00:33:00,140
Jing Kan won't die.

855
00:33:00,580 --> 00:33:01,540
Yes.

856
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:03,700
Trust me.

857
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:06,940
Yes, yes.

858
00:33:07,340 --> 00:33:08,300
Yes.

859
00:33:09,780 --> 00:33:10,940
Yes, yes.

860
00:33:11,380 --> 00:33:12,420
Trust my niece.

861
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,540
Put it down. Take it away.

862
00:33:13,540 --> 00:33:14,940
Come, come here.

863
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,380
Come to me.

864
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:27,780
(Refined Chamber)

865
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:35,220
Milord.

866
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:39,140
Slow down, slow down.

867
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:45,700
Milord.

868
00:33:45,820 --> 00:33:47,140
The Jings sent a messenger.

869
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:49,100
They want to plead for Jing Kan.

870
00:33:49,900 --> 00:33:51,100
Plead for what?

871
00:33:51,780 --> 00:33:53,220
Jing Kan's death sentence.

872
00:33:55,060 --> 00:33:56,340
His crime

873
00:33:56,340 --> 00:33:57,860
doesn't deserve death.

874
00:33:58,340 --> 00:34:00,420
Right, it doesn't, milord.

875
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:02,380
Then, which brat

876
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:03,420
sentenced him?

877
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,780
You.

878
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:10,580
(Taiping Government)

879
00:34:10,580 --> 00:34:12,540
Luckily, you came to me.

880
00:34:13,020 --> 00:34:14,260
If it were someone else,

881
00:34:14,380 --> 00:34:15,780
who could handle this?

882
00:34:15,980 --> 00:34:17,180
Yes, yes.

883
00:34:17,700 --> 00:34:18,740
Advisor Xia,

884
00:34:18,740 --> 00:34:19,900
please think of a way

